{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all employers to provide contractual sick pay on top of SSP",
        "additional_details": "Statutory Sick Pay is only \u00a3118.75 a week which we think is far below living costs.\r\n\r\nMany workers may use annual leave to cover sickness, leaving them without proper rest or holidays.\r\nThis can harm mental health and increases stress.\r\n\r\nWe think no one should have to choose between their health and paying bills. \r\nWe believe mandatory enhanced sick pay would protect workers\u2019 wellbeing and promote public health.\r\n",
        "background": "Make it a legal requirement for all employers to offer enhanced sick pay on top of Statutory Sick Pay.\r\n \r\nThis should guarantee at least partial pay for the full duration of sickness, so workers aren\u2019t - in our view - financially punished for being unwell.\r\n",
